Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:10.33,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This just got real!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:31.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Listen up, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:33.97,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, so I've got a few things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,First off,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:40.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,who here beside me thinks this is the best Equestria Games delegation in Ponyville history?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.44,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And no matter what your sport is, we've gotta give it our best,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:51.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,because we've all got a genuine shot at Ponyville gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:58.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,With the possible exception of Bulk Biceps, Fluttershy and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:00.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're good and all, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,we're up against the Wonderbolts in the aerial relay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:06.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,gold's kind of a stretch. Let's not kid ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.59,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We have absolutely no shot at winning gold either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:15.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's because you're carrying the flag for Ponyville in the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:16.79,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There are no winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:20.40,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Winners or not, we still have a chance to be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:23.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit! Hear that, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Winners or not, we all still have a chance to be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:34.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But, uh, let's still try to win lots and lots of stuff too, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's all in there, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:36.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Spike, champion gear carrier for all your gear carrier needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.07,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And ponyville flag? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What about flag pole?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,In with the portable ramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.96,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest, Applebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's just nervous, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Perfectly understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:52.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm afraid of or forget something, I start to panic, I have a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,I count to ten, and by the time I've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,I've calmed myself enough to get the job done right everytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy-cider-squeazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:03.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:04.56,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike! Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A thousand pardons, O Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.95,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Thanks for bringing Spike to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.83,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.16,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,We'll have our hoofponies go back for your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:30.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can they hang back a second and tell me what's going on first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,So the ponies here think I'm some kind of hero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,More of the green ones, please? I like the green ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Last time you were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:49.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you got the Crystal Heart to Princess Cadance in time to save this entire empire from destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.20,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,You are known throughout my empire as
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:56.49,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,"Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:57.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're a big shot here, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See that? That's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hello, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:11.14,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,This is why we all hope you do us the honor of lighting the torch of the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:16.52,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,You'd be the very first Dragon in the history of the Equestria games to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.91,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:20.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,And, bonus, I can do it with my fire breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.01,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Places for the procession, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.57,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:08.91,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,And you're {\i1}quite{\i0} certain you also understand {\i1}exactly{\i0} what you're supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,I stand where you tell me until you give me the signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,and then I walk over and light the torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.83,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Couldn't be simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.89,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Mister the dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.68,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.84,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.85,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,would somepony help him walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.14,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Now, please welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.14,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,the delegation from
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.64,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.74,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,This is the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.79,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you the signal now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.19,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Mr. the Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike! Calm yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,Count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,three...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,fourteen thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twenty thousand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Thirty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.62,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,Tell me this isn't happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Equestria, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:25.72,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Mr. the Dragon! Would you light the torch already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.95,Spike,,0,0,0,, I don't know what it is, but I just don't have the stuff today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:30.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,Did you bring a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.09,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,You're a {\i1}fire{\i0}-breathing dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then some cough drops, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nevermind. I'll keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.83,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Somepony go down and help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Light! Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.64,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.35,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Well, better late than never.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.66,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Let the games…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.12,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There they are, little superstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You were fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:44.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Made me sit up proud like a corn stalk in august.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:46.06,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You done good, squirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You three really were wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But does anypony know what was going on with Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,He sure seemed to be having a tough time of it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,He put things right in time though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't want him to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So I cast a secret spell to light it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Have you told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:08.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, but he might have figured it out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You gotta tell him, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm just afraid of how he'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know what pride he takes in a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:15.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Psst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Here he comes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.80,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Act casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,The weirdest thing happened down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:28.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:30.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, there I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,trying to light the torch with all of Equestria watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,and feeling like the the hugest failure ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,And then the thing just lit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:39.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was afraid you'd be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:43.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:44.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why would I be upset to discover that I can light fire…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.77,Spike,,0,0,0,,with my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:50.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Look, look it's the Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.48,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Can we get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,How you saved our empire last time you were here, was really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,Duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know what else is amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:13.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Once it bursts into flames from brain power, I'll send another one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,May I have a word with you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'd better be careful with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,Might burst into flames later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,The late reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:42.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I can set fire to stuff with my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,mind reading must be just around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I predict that you're about to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,to set fire to something…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,with my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:52.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:55.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,So how do you explain what happened down there in front of thousands and thousands of…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I did it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I cast a spell to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,In front of…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,thousands…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,and thousands…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:11.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stand to see you stuck like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,I need to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:26.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,You should probably ask somebody special instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.22,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Our next event,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.60,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,The aerial relay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's Dash and Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.82,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.87,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We can't be late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Miss, step right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:54.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Unicorns will no longer be admitted without a disabling spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,To prevent cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And make sure you don't even try casting a spell or we'll know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If Ponyville medals here, we have eight medals so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,putting us tied to the lead with Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Unless Cloudsdale medals here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Miss Harshwhinny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you're really busy, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.90,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's something else I can do for the Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know, something really worthy of the Crystal Empire's admiration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.38,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.76,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,You lit the torch for the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:52.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:53.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,that wasn't really…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.68,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,That wasn't worthy enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.06,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,For pony's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:01.53,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know you'll be asking to put on a rock concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.64,RevizorReal,,0,0,0,,Celebrities…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We got silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.39,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to all our medalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.38,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,And now, the anthem of…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I shall do the honor of singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:36.23,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Spike, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,You know how they always just play the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I know all the words to our anthem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,and will sing them for you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,loud and proud to the enjoyment of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.23,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.92,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,the Cloudsdale anthem as sung by…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.13,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,The Cloudsdale anthem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:02.32,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,They only play the anthem for the winner, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.44,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are from Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,But I don't know the words to the Cloudsdale anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,I've never even heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.95,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sing for us, oh Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:23.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're the Wonderbolts and we're super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:27.24,Spike,,0,0,0,,And we're from Cloudsdale, which-is-a-part-of-Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,That we like best, and we're proud and we're fast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,and we like it because it really has nice trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we love the town because it's so cool, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:41.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,And we like to fly really fast and everything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,I kinda wish this was over 'cause it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,isn't… yet… over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Now…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're the Wonderbolts and we're super fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,And we're cloud from Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:59.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,We like it there 'cause it's really nice and the trees are cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I hope it is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:05.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,And... it keeps going on, la la la
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,And we really love the town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:14.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,So I wish that this... song... was over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Over... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Over... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.41,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Spike, you comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nah, I got this stuff to pack up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.62,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,But you've been moping in here for almost the entire Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.12,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And tonight's the closing ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Which means we leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ergo, the packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.47,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,And so the Games conclude as they always do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:06.78,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,with the ice archery finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.51,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Ice archers, take your places!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.11,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Too bad Ponyville doesn't have any ice archers competin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.96,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We don't have anyone to root for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:20.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's okay. Ponyville has thirty seven medals, and Cloudsdale thirty six,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:24.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,so looks like we'll be medal champs of the Games anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But Cloudsdale has two ice archery finalists down there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:32.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If they both place, Cloudsale wins the medal count!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.23,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that it all comes down to this one event?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:38.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Omigoshomigoshomigoshomigosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:44.55,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Come take this extra seat next to me and freak out over the medal count!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.94,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,omigoshomigoshomigoshomigosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was looking for Spike. Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.80,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.28,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We tried to talk him into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.93,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,...but he wouldn't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:57.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You can have his extra seat, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:16:59.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm super-busy! Look at all this packing left to do, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:17.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:21.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No more hiding out. You're coming with me. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can I at least wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Those aren't your average arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They freeze whatever part of the target they hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:39.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whoever encases their entire target in ice first wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:44.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Keep your eye on number seven from Cloudsdale – he's the favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Spike, I don't see why you're being so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,I let everypony down, twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:59.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,You never let anypony down, so you don't have any idea what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? I've totally let ponies down. That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:08.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The torch got lit, the aerial relay teams got their medals, no harm no foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:11.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can we at least watch from inside there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I'm ready to face crowds in the stands just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.50,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:43.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Steer it towards the field, away from the crowds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.94,Shining_Armor,,0,0,0,,Somepony cut the disabling spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,There isn't time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Dash, Fluttershy! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:27.27,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you personally for saving those ponies and the Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.54,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,O Great and Honorable Spike the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.82,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,You must be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.48,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You guess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:39.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,I just saw what needed to be done and reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just so happens I can breathe fire and... if any of you could do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,you'd have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:47.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for bein' blunt, Spike, but you're not makin' a lick of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:56.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You keep saying you let everypony down, but we all keep saying you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You know who's disappointed in you, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:02.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You. And only you can make it right with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What would that take, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can we turn back time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'd sure like a do-over on that opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.78,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,We can't turn back time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:18.77,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,but, would you do me the great honor of lighting fireworks in my place
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.09,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,at the closing ceremonies tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike. You saved the Crystal Empire, twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:27.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think you can light some fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to at least give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:42.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We did it! Ponyville won the medal count,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and only by one medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,wonder which medal that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:54.71,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to have opened the best Equestria Games in Ponyville history, squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:57.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Probably as good as it feels to close them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, it's kinda weird. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:10.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how many times others tell you you're great, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:14.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all the praise in the world means nothing if you don't feel it inside. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:22.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes to feel good about yourself, you gotta let go of the past. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That way, when the time comes to let your greatness fly, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll be able to light up the whole sky.{\i0}
